FBIS4-63338 "drsov099_v_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-099 Daily Report 19 May 1994 Lithuania Trade Unions Stage Protest Actions in Major Cities Trade Unions Stage Protest Actions in Major Cities LD2005164294 Vilnius Radio Vilnius in English 2130 GMT 19 May 94 LD2005164294 Vilnius Radio Vilnius English BFN [Excerpt] The Lithuanian trade unions staged an action of protest under the slogan against poverty, in all the major cities of Lithuania. In Vilnius, the protestors gathered in the municipality square to demonstrate against what they called the government's policy of economic and social genocide in Lithuania. According to the organizers of the protest action the living standards of the majority of Lithuania's population are going down at a catastrophic speed, while the level of unemployment is increasing [words indistinct]. [passage omitted]
